&lt;h4&gt;
    In databases
&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
    Requirements Management tools and Change Request tools are an option to capture the list of work to be done.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
    As part of the Project Plan
&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
    Instead of being&amp;nbsp;represented in a separate artifact, this list&amp;nbsp;can be represented as a section on the project
    plan, containing the same columns as above.
